content.text: Hi I'm not married either , have you ever wondered why ?
I have no interest in marriage .

Sorry to hear that . I like to go to farmer's markets with my friends because we can explore new foods and find fresh produce.
I like to read a lot too . One of my favorite shows is Face Off on Syfy .
I've never heard of that show . What's it about ?
It 's a show where people compete to create special fx makeup.
It is . I love all the creative designs .
I'm not very creative so I have to admire people who are .
That 's okay . I like to see the world in a different way .
I do too . I think that 's why I like going to farmer's markets . I like to try new things .
I love exploring new places . I wish I could travel more .
Me too . I 'm hoping to go to Europe someday .
That would be amazing ! I would love to see all the historic landmarks .
